item.description: Kelly Spalding Home is a place for inspiration and encouragement to create a home for family, friends and entertaining. No matter the budget, I truly believe all it takes is some helpful guidance and a great vision for your house to become your home one room at a time. My philosophy as a decorator and stylist is to help you make your space YOURS! I am very intentional about surrounding you with things that matter to you, not the latest trends. We all want a soft place to land and to be surrounded by comfort and love and I believe that a home should wrap it's arms around you when you enter the front door.
